            {
               "text": "### Imagens de British Museum\n\nEstas imagens são protegidas por direitos autorais de British Museum e permitidas para uso de acordo com a licença determinada por eles.\n\nPara visualizar todas as imagens, use as setas esquerda e direita no slide abaixo.",
               "source": null,
               "date_time": null,
               "isTable": false,
               "imgdesc": "",
               "format": "markdown",
               "PostMention": ""
            },
            {
               "text": "<p><div class=\"htSlides\"><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">1 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPhoenician\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPhoenician', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Texto fenício presente no museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite0> ).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Playing with Consonants and Vowels (Literature)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">2 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBanner\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBanner', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Banner em estilo semelhante ao encontrado na tumba de Wu Zetian (武則天). © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite1>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">3 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAtra\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAtra', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tablet Babilônico sobre o Dilúvio. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite2>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>The Origin of the Universe (Atlas)</li><li>Do literature and science not communicate? (Myths Believes)</li><li>Has there never been a flood? (Myths Believes)</li><li>What is the extent of the impact of the flood? (Myths Believes)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">4 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBuda\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBuda', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">O Tablet do Dilúvio. © Trustees of the British Museum ().</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">5 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBritishMuseum0\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBritishMuseum0', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cesta oblonga de junco trançado. © Trustees of the British Museum (). Shared under a <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/4.0/\" target=\"_blank\">Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International (CC BY-NC-SA 4.0)</a>.</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">6 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGilgamesh\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGilgamesh', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Lista de Reis de Abydos. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite3>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Do literature and science not communicate? (Myths Believes)</li><li>Has there never been a flood? (Myths Believes)</li><li>Is it possible to live in the sky? Is the Earth flat? (Myths Believes)</li><li>What is the extent of the impact of the flood? (Myths Believes)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">7 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgMid001\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMid001', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Diferentes tipos de vasos, expostos no Museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite4> ).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Cradles of civilization (Parte II) (History)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">8 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgEgypt\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgEgypt', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cilindro de Ciro. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite5> ).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>The Writing System (Literature)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">9 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPottery1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPottery1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Mapa do mundo habitável. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite6>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">10 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCylinder\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCylinder', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tablete encontrado em Tell Al-'Ubaid. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite7>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">11 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgB', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Astrolábio que mostra um calendário com os meses em latim, presente no Museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite8> ).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Comparing Worlds (Atlas)</li><li>The Ancient Babylonian World Map (Atlas)</li><li>Cradles of civilization (Part I) (History)</li><li>Anachronism (Literature)</li><li>Equality Levels (Literature)</li><li>Did texts written in Mesopotamia describe the world we know today? (Myths Believes)</li><li>Has there never been a flood? (Myths Believes)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">12 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgT1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgT1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Moeda da dinastia Tang do ano de <htdate0>, no museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite9> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">13 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgAstro\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgAstro', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Épico de Lugalbanda. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite10>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Organizing time (Physics)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">14 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCoin\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCoin', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Tábua de argila com os materiais necessários para os barcos de Magan. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite11>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">15 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgLugalbanda\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgLugalbanda', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Cone dedicatório. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite12>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">16 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgMagan\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgMagan', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Contas de Vidro. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite13>).</div><div class=\"htSlideRefs\"><b>Related content:</b><ul><li>Understanding the Multiplication Table (6 and 7) (First Steps)</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">17 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgCD\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgCD', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Selo cilíndrico de <i>Meskalamdug</i>. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite14>).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">18 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgGB\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgGB', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Vaso decorado com marcas de corda, exposto no museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite15> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">19 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgSuanpan\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgSuanpan', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Projétil de ponta de Clóvis exposto no Museu Britânico. © Trustees of the British Museum ( ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">20 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgC1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgC1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Ponta de flecha feita com osso contendo inscrição. © Trustees of the British Museum (<htcite16> ).</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">21 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgBritishMuseum1\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgBritishMuseum1', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\">Prisma da Enciclopédia de Ashurbanipal. © Trustees of the British Museum ().</div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">22 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPottery\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPottery', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">23 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPoint\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPoint', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">24 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgXuanzong\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgXuanzong', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">25 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgChinese\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgChinese', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><div class=\"htSlide\"><div class=\"htSlideCounter\">26 / 26</div><img class=\"imgGameSize\" id=\"imgPBM\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPBM', '0%')\"><div class=\"htSlideCaption\"></div></div><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-left htSlidePrev\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(-1);\"></i><i class=\"fa-solid fa-chevron-right htSlideNext\" onclick=\"htPlusDivs(1);\"></i></div></p>",
